<h1>New Post</h1>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span4">
    <p>Guidelines for new posts:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Titles must be at least 5 characters long.</li>
      <li>Descriptions must be at least 20 characters long.</li>
      <li>Make sure content is appropriate.</li>
      <li>Inappropriate content will be removed.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="span8">
    <%= render partial: 'form', locals: { topic: @topic, post: @post } %>
  </div>
</div>
